<blockquote>
  <p><code>RequestInterface</code>, <code>ServerRequestInterface</code>, <code>ResponseInterface</code> extend <code>MessageInterface</code>  because the <code>Request</code> and the <code>Response</code> are <code>HTTP Messages</code>.
When using <code>ServerRequestInterface</code>, both <code>RequestInterface</code> and <code>Psr\Http\Message\MessageInterface</code> methods are considered.</p>
</blockquote>

